Package: MinirhizotronR
Type: Package
Title: Minirhizotron Root Scan Depth Resolved Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Johannes Cunow
Maintainer: Johannes Cunow <johannes.cunow@gmail.com>
Description: This package calculates some metrics related to depth distribion to an minirhizotron scan. It relies on outside handling of Image Segmentation. The package was tested with 'RootDetector' by Peters et al. 2023 Scientific Reports 13
